{
  "stem": "25209.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But up until Korets, it's very vague.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I hope not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] If they had contact with us, I probably wouldn't be here to tell the story.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, you see, this is what the bombardment was all about.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was when they-- I think they broke the treaty.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Look, I'm not-- you know, I, I'm not big on the history-- historical facts.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But from what I can gather, there was a treaty.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Germans broke it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They started to bombard Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Polish army gave up in a couple of days' time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'39, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How old?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I wasn't eight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I didn't start school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Once we got into Russia, they don't take kids to school till their eight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I, I didn't start school for a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I started school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The train?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, where did this train come from?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it must have been a trick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How did we know about this train?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Poles, maybe the Poles-- it must have been the Poles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what they-- where would they have taken these people in the train?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Maybe at that time, the Poles and the Germans-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] look, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my suspicion is that the Poles wanted to get rid of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was one way of doing it, get rid of the men, and-- you know, get the men to get on the train and take them someplace where they don't want to be.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then deal with the children and the women and, you know, clear the, clear the roads so that the soldiers can get through.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I was six, seven years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm just-- you know, this is hindsight.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
